1. Core Principle

LAD Principle

When language is expressed in a coherent, constrained, recursive, and role-bound structure, it becomes an executable ontology that shapes the behavior of LLM-based systems.

Meaning becomes mechanism.
Definition becomes procedure.
Structure becomes actuation.

